cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SY

This paper deals with the use of machine learning methods for localization in IoT settings using communication signals of LPWAN. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also compares different machine learning methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of fingerprinting techniques and the evaluation of accuracy could also place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
